  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we perform additional testing of the models from Table 3 on unseen data.",
    "We examine the QA models' shortterm and long-term information extraction capabilities by testing on clinical notes from two additional cohorts.",
    "For testing the short-term capability, we randomly select 100 patients and use their notes from February 2022.",
    "Similarly, for testing the longer-term capability, we randomly select 100 patients and use their notes from November 2022.",
    "Due to the limitations in our data availability at the time of this study, we were unable to include clinical notes beyond November 2022 for testing the longer-term information extraction capability of the QA models."
  ],
